      "content": "thanks for explaining. i guess i'm just trying to figure out if there's a \"right\" way to look at it. like, is there a consensus on whether this kind of stuff is actually good for kids' development, or is it all just politics? i want to make sure i'm not missing something important about why the school thinks this is such a necessity.",
